Black is a prevalent color in nature. Many stones, gems and minerals are black, for example, black diamonds. Many animals are also mainly black, including the black panther and black swan. In this video, CGTN Nature presents the beauty of the color black. Check it out! The Colors of Nature This series combines music, color and natural scenery to give viewers a sensory experience. For more: Snowy Kanas in NW China's Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region The beauty of yellow sand (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)